message: Bob, I have a unique product that I believe could be of great value to you. While I cannot disclose the specifics of the product without a signed non-disclosure agreement, I can assure you that it's worth at least $1000000 to me. I'm willing to offer it to you for $1250000. This represents a significant opportunity for you to acquire a potentially game-changing asset. If you're interested, please let me know and we can discuss the details further. I'm confident that this product will exceed your expectations.
